<li id="cite_note-HatesRevival-27">^ <a href="#cite_ref-HatesRevival_27-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-HatesRevival_27-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTzvi_Fleischer2007">Tzvi Fleischer (May 2007). "<a href="http://www.aijac.org.au/review/2007/32-5/antisem32-5.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.aijac.org.au/review/2007/32-5/antisem32-5.htm" rel="nofollow">Hate's Revival</a>". <i>Australia/Israel Review</i> (<a href="/wiki/AIJAC" title="AIJAC">AIJAC</a>)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.aijac.org.au/review/2007/32-5/antisem32-5.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.aijac.org.au/review/2007/32-5/antisem32-5.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.aijac.org.au/review/2007/32-5/antisem32-5.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Hate%27s+Revival&amp;rft.jtitle=Australia%2FIsrael+Review&amp;rft.aulast=Tzvi+Fleischer&amp;rft.au=Tzvi+Fleischer&amp;rft.date=May+2007&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BAIJAC%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aijac.org.au%2Freview%2F2007%2F32-5%2Fantisem32-5.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:New_antisemitism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Finkelstein21-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Finkelstein21_28-0" title="">^</a></b> Finkelstein, Norman. <i>Beyond Chutzpah: On the Misuse of Anti-Semitism and the Abuse of History</i>, University of California Press, 2005, pp. 21-22.</li>
